description:
Ready to dive into the fascinating world of Noam Chomsky? In this short and snappy video, we bring you 7 fun facts about the legendary philosopher, linguist, and political thinker. From his groundbreaking contributions to linguistics to his influence on modern thought, you'll discover why Chomsky is one of the most important intellectuals of our time.

Learn something new in under 60 seconds, and don’t forget to hit the like button, share with your friends, and subscribe for more fun facts about the world’s greatest thinkers!
